    noria:alarmProposedRepairAction <https://w3id.org/noria/op_DBRestart> ;
    noria:alarmMonitoredAttribute <https://w3id.org/noria/instance_MonitoredAttr_CPUUsage> ;
    noria:alarmMitigatedBy <https://w3id.org/noria/event_db_restart_action> .

