# --- Using noria:structuralObservableOf (inverse of noria:structuralElementProperty) ---
# noria:structuralElementObservable is a subproperty of noria:elementProperty, which is a subproperty of seas:hasProperty.
# noria:structuralObservableOf is inverse of noria:structuralElementProperty.
# So, if a Resource has a virtualServerStatus (which is a structuralElementObservable), then the status is structuralObservableOf the Resource.
# Let's explicitly create a StructuralObservable instance and link it.

<https://w3id.org/noria/observable_DB01_CPUStatus>
    a noria:StructuralObservable ;
    rdfs:label "DB01 CPU Status Observable"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "An observable property representing the CPU status of DB01."@en ;
    noria:structuralObservableOf <https://w3id.org/noria/instance_ServerVM_DB01> .

<https://w3id.org/noria/observable_CR1_InterfaceStatus>
    a noria:StructuralObservable ;
    rdfs:label "CR1 Eth0/0/0 Status Observable"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "An observable property representing the operational status of Core Router 1's Ethernet 0/0/0 interface."@en ;
    noria:structuralObservableOf <https://w3id.org/noria/ni_CoreRouter1_Eth0_0> .

# --- Using noria:actionCorrelatedOperationPlan ---
# This property links a CorrectiveMaintenanceAction or ChangeAction to an OperationPlan.
# The schema doesn't define CorrectiveMaintenanceAction or ChangeAction directly, but they are mentioned in comments for pep:ProcedureExecutionContainer.
# I will create dummy instances of these classes (as subclasses of pep:ProcedureExecutionContainer or pep:ProcedureExecution) to demonstrate the property.

<https://w3id.org/noria/action_DBRestartExecution>
    a pep:ProcedureExecution ; # pep:ProcedureExecution is a subclass of pep:ProcedureExecutionContainer
    rdfs:label "DB Restart Execution"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "An execution instance of the database restart operation plan."@en ;
    noria:actionCorrelatedOperationPlan noria:op_DBRestart .

<https://w3id.org/noria/action_SFPReplacementExecution>
    a pep:ProcedureExecution ;
    rdfs:label "SFP Replacement Execution"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "An execution instance of the SFP module replacement operation plan."@en ;
    noria:actionCorrelatedOperationPlan noria:op_SFPReplacement .

<https://w3id.org/noria/action_RouterFirmwareUpgradeExecution>
    a pep:ProcedureExecution ;
    rdfs:label "Router Firmware Upgrade Execution"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "An execution instance of the router firmware upgrade operation plan."@en ;
    noria:actionCorrelatedOperationPlan noria:op_RouterFirmwareUpgrade .
